WEBVTT

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:19.450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}The Apothecary Diaries</b></font>

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:19.450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}The Apothecary <font color="#000000">Diaries</font></b></font>

00:01:31.480 --> 00:01:34.490
<font size="10">{\an1}This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on
 are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.</font>

00:01:40.030 --> 00:01:43.990
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}<font size="17">Episode 32: The Empress Dowager</font></font>

00:01:43.390 --> 00:01:45.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Starting today, this will be your room.</font>

00:01:46.180 --> 00:01:47.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A storage shed...</font>

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:50.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You really want me to use this place?</font>

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:53.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. Think about what you did.</font>

00:01:56.310 --> 00:01:59.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Yinghua, are you all right?</font>

00:02:01.720 --> 00:02:06.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How could I be?! I can't believe 
you collect those things!</font>

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:09.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">One of these days, Lady Hongniang 
will kick you out of your room,</font>

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:11.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and transfer you to a storage shed!</font>

00:02:13.370 --> 00:02:14.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That sounds good.</font>

00:02:15.130 --> 00:02:15.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh?</font>

00:02:16.130 --> 00:02:18.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The storage shed is bigger 
than my current room,</font>

00:02:18.990 --> 00:02:21.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and I could make noise at night...</font>

00:02:21.210 --> 00:02:22.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao?</font>

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:23.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah, it's a good idea.</font>

00:02:24.340 --> 00:02:26.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In that case, let's get going.</font>

00:02:26.580 --> 00:02:28.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I have to go back and ask Lady Hongniang.</font>

00:02:28.990 --> 00:02:32.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What? Wait! Wait!</font>

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:40.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What in the...</font>

00:02:43.690 --> 00:02:45.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Think about what you've done!</font>

00:02:45.630 --> 00:02:47.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Hongniang...</font>

00:02:47.220 --> 00:02:49.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you so much!</font>

00:02:49.710 --> 00:02:51.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is where I'll hang herbs!</font>

00:02:51.100 --> 00:02:52.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is where I'll make medicine!</font>

00:02:52.810 --> 00:02:55.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That goes here! This goes there!</font>

00:02:56.550 --> 00:02:59.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I told you so! It's pointless!</font>

00:03:00.410 --> 00:03:03.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The storage shed? Unbelievable!</font>

00:03:04.180 --> 00:03:09.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You told on her to Lady Hongniang? 
Didn't you go a bit too far, Yinghua?</font>

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:14.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It wasn't me! Maomao asked 
Lady Hongniang herself!</font>

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:16.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Right, Maomao?</font>

00:03:16.340 --> 00:03:19.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. It works out for me in several ways.</font>

00:03:19.010 --> 00:03:20.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh?</font>

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:23.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">At any rate, Maomao...</font>

00:03:23.740 --> 00:03:26.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Stop collecting insects, okay?</font>

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:30.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Insects? What I'm collecting are lizard tails.</font>

00:03:31.090 --> 00:03:34.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Besides, I stopped gathering 
them after you collapsed.</font>

00:03:35.640 --> 00:03:36.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Really?</font>

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:39.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But there's a rumor going around</font>

00:03:39.160 --> 00:03:42.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">that a weird court lady is catching
 bugs while laughing to herself.</font>

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:44.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I don't do that.</font>

00:03:44.740 --> 00:03:47.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There was that one time I was 
collecting moths as part of a job,</i></font>

00:03:47.370 --> 00:03:49.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but laughing while chasing insects...</i></font>

00:03:54.890 --> 00:03:57.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is a serious issue.</font>

00:03:57.880 --> 00:04:01.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh? Hfff I hmmg Hinmhi mmghi?</font>

00:04:01.660 --> 00:04:04.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah, Shisui. Have you seen her recently?</font>

00:04:05.570 --> 00:04:10.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Shisui, huh? She can be a real phantom...</font>

00:04:13.710 --> 00:04:17.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey, does anyone know where Shisui is?</font>

00:04:17.780 --> 00:04:21.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Shisui? I might have seen her, 
but I might have not...</font>

00:04:21.800 --> 00:04:24.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh? Where was she? Tell me, please!</font>

00:04:25.090 --> 00:04:28.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well... Um...</font>

00:04:28.870 --> 00:04:32.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Oh, I bet they're being cautious 
because I serve a concubine directly.</i></font>

00:04:34.200 --> 00:04:39.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Xiaolan is actually the rare one 
for talking to anyone openly.</i></font>

00:04:40.110 --> 00:04:42.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Do I have anything on me to use as a gift?</i></font>

00:04:43.260 --> 00:04:44.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Oh, here we go.</i></font>

00:04:44.830 --> 00:04:49.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Depending on the information, 
I could give you this...</font>

00:04:50.200 --> 00:04:50.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Use this.</font>

00:04:51.380 --> 00:04:52.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're bleeding.</font>

00:04:56.060 --> 00:04:57.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Th-This scent...</font>

00:04:57.810 --> 00:05:00.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Could it be his...?!</font>

00:05:00.940 --> 00:05:02.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll leave that up to your imagination.</font>

00:05:03.770 --> 00:05:06.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, is there anything you can tell me?</font>

00:05:10.500 --> 00:05:15.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>They said she's usually out 
in the thicket on the north side, but...</i></font>

00:05:15.570 --> 00:05:18.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I think this was where I ran 
into her the last time, too.</i></font>

00:05:18.250 --> 00:05:20.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is this her favorite spot?</i></font>

00:05:26.280 --> 00:05:29.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I should have brought a mosquito repellent.</font>

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:31.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">White blossom...</font>

00:05:32.420 --> 00:05:34.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, this is where they grow.</font>

00:05:36.310 --> 00:05:41.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>When I was little, I used to collect 
white blossom seeds with the courtesans.</i></font>

00:05:42.250 --> 00:05:45.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Not for using the powder inside for make-up,</i></font>

00:05:45.690 --> 00:05:47.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but to make an abortion drug.</i></font>

00:05:50.410 --> 00:05:53.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Shin didn't wear any perfume at first.</i></font>

00:05:54.090 --> 00:05:57.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Since she was trying to take 
Concubine Lihua's place,</i></font>

00:05:57.560 --> 00:06:01.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>it wouldn't be strange for Shin to avoid 
perfume, which could lead to miscarriages.</i></font>

00:06:01.780 --> 00:06:06.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Still, Shin risked wearing perfume so 
she could secretly make abortion drugs.</i></font>

00:06:06.170 --> 00:06:07.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's probably because...</i></font>

00:06:08.470 --> 00:06:13.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Lady Gyokuyou isn't the only one 
receiving the love of the emperor.</i></font>

00:06:13.510 --> 00:06:16.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's possible that Lady Lihua 
is pregnant as well.</i></font>

00:06:18.330 --> 00:06:22.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But that's not the only mystery 
I noted from that incident.</i></font>

00:06:22.830 --> 00:06:27.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The abortion drug made by courtesans 
uses, in addition to the white blossom,</i></font>

00:06:27.060 --> 00:06:32.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>other ingredients like lantern plant, 
peony, balsam, and mercury.</i></font>

00:06:32.750 --> 00:06:37.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Aside from mercury, the other ingredients
 can be found in the rear palace.</i></font>

00:06:37.510 --> 00:06:41.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Even though she could 
have gotten them here,</i></font>

00:06:41.390 --> 00:06:44.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Shin got her abortion drug 
ingredients through the caravan.</i></font>

00:06:44.100 --> 00:06:44.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>In other words,</i></font>

00:06:45.460 --> 00:06:50.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Shin had no knowledge of medicine, 
and someone taught her how to make poison.</i></font>

00:06:50.970 --> 00:06:54.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>And that someone is probably 
still here, in the rear palace...</i></font>

00:06:59.710 --> 00:07:01.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Found you!</font>

00:07:02.020 --> 00:07:05.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hold it right there, you! Hold it!</font>

00:07:05.080 --> 00:07:08.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This is who they confused me for? How rude.</i></font>

00:07:09.210 --> 00:07:10.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Got you!</font>

00:07:20.250 --> 00:07:21.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Insect!</font>

00:07:22.640 --> 00:07:23.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh...</font>

00:07:23.980 --> 00:07:27.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Shisui, it'd be great if you could let go...</font>

00:07:32.260 --> 00:07:34.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sorry about that, Maomao.</font>

00:07:34.290 --> 00:07:35.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's fine.</font>

00:07:35.940 --> 00:07:38.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Were those the insects you were hunting?</font>

00:07:38.850 --> 00:07:39.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes!</font>

00:07:39.940 --> 00:07:41.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She must really love bugs.</i></font>

00:07:50.030 --> 00:07:53.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This insect is native to
 the island nation in the east!</font>

00:07:53.400 --> 00:07:55.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They make noise by rubbing 
their wings together!</font>

00:07:55.320 --> 00:07:58.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It was probably part of 
some trade goods, but escaped!</font>

00:07:58.410 --> 00:08:01.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I think this is the only place you can find
 them, like the moths from the other day!</font>

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:05.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They do have a similar color as cockroaches, 
but they're different, don't worry!</font>

00:08:05.370 --> 00:08:07.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And also! And also! And also!</font>

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:09.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I shouldn't have asked.</i></font>

00:08:13.750 --> 00:08:15.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What's that sound?</i></font>

00:08:24.580 --> 00:08:27.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is that... the empress dowager?</font>

00:08:27.880 --> 00:08:30.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Last I saw her was 
at the garden party last year.</i></font>

00:08:30.420 --> 00:08:31.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She really does look young.</i></font>

00:08:32.680 --> 00:08:35.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hard to believe she's the emperor's mother...</i></font>

00:08:36.780 --> 00:08:38.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why are you hiding?</font>

00:08:38.340 --> 00:08:40.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why are you?</font>

00:08:40.110 --> 00:08:42.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, it's kind of reflexive.</font>

00:08:43.230 --> 00:08:45.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wonder if she's going to the clinic?</font>

00:08:45.510 --> 00:08:46.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Clinic?</font>

00:08:46.700 --> 00:08:50.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah, it's an unofficial clinic 
run by court ladies.</font>

00:08:50.980 --> 00:08:52.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I know about that.</font>

00:08:52.420 --> 00:08:55.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Apparently, the empress dowager 
was the one who founded it.</font>

00:08:55.620 --> 00:08:56.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The empress dowager?</font>

00:08:57.350 --> 00:09:00.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This was back when the empress 
had a lot of power,</font>

00:09:00.250 --> 00:09:02.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">so the empress dowager 
couldn't make it official.</font>

00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:04.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:09:05.390 --> 00:09:09.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The empress dowager is really kind.</font>

00:09:11.710 --> 00:09:18.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Also, they say she was behind 
the banning of slaves and eunuchs.</font>

00:09:18.330 --> 00:09:19.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:24.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>From a humanitarian perspective, 
banning slaves was probably a good idea.</i></font>

00:09:24.810 --> 00:09:28.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But, aside from slaves 
who are treated like animals,</i></font>

00:09:28.890 --> 00:09:32.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>there are some, like courtesans, who use 
their bodies as collateral to borrow money.</i></font>

00:09:32.910 --> 00:09:35.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This is legal, and considered 
to be similar to employment.</i></font>

00:09:36.070 --> 00:09:40.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>However, seen from the outside, 
courtesans could appear to be slaves as well.</i></font>

00:09:41.250 --> 00:09:45.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The old lady said when the bans were 
announced, she felt a chill down her spine.</i></font>

00:09:45.720 --> 00:09:48.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Officially, slavery is banned, 
but in practice,</i></font>

00:09:48.680 --> 00:09:52.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>everyone knows it still exists
under a different name.</i></font>

00:09:53.590 --> 00:09:56.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, I'd better get going.</font>

00:09:56.980 --> 00:10:00.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao, you probably shouldn't be wasting 
too much time outside either, right?</font>

00:10:00.260 --> 00:10:02.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, yeah, but...</font>

00:10:03.750 --> 00:10:06.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Does the empress dowager visiting 
the clinic have anything to do with</i></font>

00:10:06.730 --> 00:10:10.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>what happened at 
the Crystal Pavilion the other day?</i></font>

00:10:11.530 --> 00:10:13.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If the empress dowager is on the case,</i></font>

00:10:13.700 --> 00:10:17.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>there could be a big reform 
in the medical system in the rear palace.</i></font>

00:10:17.470 --> 00:10:20.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If that's what's being discussed, 
I'd love to listen in, but...</i></font>

00:10:23.380 --> 00:10:24.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Nah, I'm going home.</font>

00:10:26.050 --> 00:10:28.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I've been causing a lot of upset lately...</i></font>

00:10:29.740 --> 00:10:30.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do over!</font>

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:31.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes...</font>

00:10:33.100 --> 00:10:34.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This is the third time.</i></font>

00:10:34.780 --> 00:10:38.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I was wondering if I was starting 
to get bullied now, but...</i></font>

00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:39.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pay attention!</font>

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:40.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes!</font>

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:41.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There!</font>

00:10:41.400 --> 00:10:42.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes!</font>

00:10:42.270 --> 00:10:44.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The other ladies-in-waiting 
are getting nitpicked, too...</i></font>

00:10:44.700 --> 00:10:48.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Be extra careful this time! 
I don't want to see a speck of dust!</font>

00:10:48.770 --> 00:10:51.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What's going on? Is someone coming to visit?</i></font>

00:10:54.780 --> 00:10:57.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's been a while, Lady Anshi.</font>

00:11:00.980 --> 00:11:03.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It was the empress dowager!</i></font>

00:11:04.410 --> 00:11:06.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you well?</font>

00:11:06.890 --> 00:11:09.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you for your compassion.</font>

00:11:09.370 --> 00:11:13.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>So, the empress dowager knows 
that Lady Gyokuyou is pregnant.</i></font>

00:11:13.810 --> 00:11:16.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I guess she must be really trustworthy.</i></font>

00:11:21.740 --> 00:11:26.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This feels more like "two friends a few 
years apart," not "wife and mother-in-law."</i></font>

00:11:27.820 --> 00:11:28.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You there.</font>

00:11:30.230 --> 00:11:33.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're the lady-in-waiting assigned here 
from Jinshi's place, yes?</font>

00:11:33.890 --> 00:11:35.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, I am.</font>

00:11:35.940 --> 00:11:37.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>How does she know that?</i></font>

00:11:37.620 --> 00:11:43.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Suiren told me. She said a girl worth 
training had gone back to the rear palace.</font>

00:11:43.140 --> 00:11:46.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She used to be my lady-in-waiting, you know.</font>

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:53.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see. That wily lady-in-waiting and 
the empress dowager know each other.</font>

00:11:59.310 --> 00:12:02.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Anshi, I beg your pardon.</font>

00:12:02.380 --> 00:12:06.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It seems Lingli is tired. 
May I put her to bed?</font>

00:12:07.420 --> 00:12:09.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, of course.</font>

00:12:13.620 --> 00:12:17.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She really can take a hint.</font>

00:12:19.090 --> 00:12:21.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please, take a seat.</font>

00:12:22.140 --> 00:12:22.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes...</font>

00:12:24.920 --> 00:12:29.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I hear you go around solving problems.</font>

00:12:31.730 --> 00:12:35.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I merely voice facts from 
my limited pool of knowledge</font>

00:12:35.230 --> 00:12:38.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">that I feel are appropriate for the situation.</font>

00:12:41.020 --> 00:12:43.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Did that sound too negative?</i></font>

00:12:43.810 --> 00:12:48.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But I don't have an incredible imagination 
or the deep knowledge my dad has.</i></font>

00:12:49.860 --> 00:12:52.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I have to tell her beforehand, 
otherwise I'd feel uneasy.</i></font>

00:12:53.260 --> 00:12:56.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's just the way I do things.</i></font>

00:13:00.570 --> 00:13:02.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's fine.</font>

00:13:06.120 --> 00:13:11.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I just want you to do your best 
to look into something.</font>

00:13:15.000 --> 00:13:16.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Did I...</font>

00:13:18.910 --> 00:13:22.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">put a curse on the late emperor?</font>

00:13:40.200 --> 00:13:42.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A curse, huh?</font>

00:13:42.530 --> 00:13:46.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Perhaps it's natural for someone 
to think that way.</i></font>

00:13:46.910 --> 00:13:51.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>To be honest, I've only ever heard people 
speak poorly of the previous emperor.</i></font>

00:13:51.660 --> 00:13:55.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"Foolish emperor," "idiot ruler," 
"puppet of the empress."</i></font>

00:13:55.650 --> 00:14:00.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The one most famous in the rear palace 
would probably be "pedophile".</i></font>

00:14:01.740 --> 00:14:04.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Taking a very young wife 
as part of a political marriage</i></font>

00:14:04.100 --> 00:14:06.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>or for collateral on a loan is not unheard of.</i></font>

00:14:06.650 --> 00:14:11.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>However, the last emperor deliberately 
chose the youngest girls available,</i></font>

00:14:11.070 --> 00:14:13.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>despite being surrounded by women 
of a more appropriate age.</i></font>

00:14:15.290 --> 00:14:17.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The empress dowager has a scar on her stomach.</i></font>

00:14:18.730 --> 00:14:21.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>When she gave birth to the current emperor,</i></font>

00:14:21.260 --> 00:14:24.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>the empress dowager was not yet mature.</i></font>

00:14:24.790 --> 00:14:27.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>They had to cut her belly 
open to retrieve the baby.</i></font>

00:14:27.470 --> 00:14:30.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The unfortunate doctor 
who had to become a eunuch</i></font>

00:14:30.490 --> 00:14:35.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>to help with that surgery was Luomen, my dad.</i></font>

00:14:35.890 --> 00:14:40.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Thanks perhaps to those sacrifices, the 
current emperor grew up strong and healthy,</i></font>

00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:43.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>and the empress dowager later gave birth 
to her second son, the imperial brother.</i></font>

00:14:44.250 --> 00:14:48.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If I remember correctly, 
the brother is one year older than me.</i></font>

00:14:48.490 --> 00:14:51.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The empress dowager must have been 
approaching thirty years old at that point.</i></font>

00:14:52.420 --> 00:14:54.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Obviously no longer a little girl.</i></font>

00:14:55.330 --> 00:14:56.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Which means...</i></font>

00:14:58.060 --> 00:15:01.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is the imperial brother really 
the son of the previous emperor...?</i></font>

00:15:03.380 --> 00:15:06.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If I said that out loud, I could be beheaded.</i></font>

00:15:10.380 --> 00:15:12.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A few days later, the empress dowager</i></font>

00:15:12.800 --> 00:15:17.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>invited the four high-ranking 
concubines to a tea party.</i></font>

00:15:17.740 --> 00:15:19.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This way, Lady Gyokuyou.</font>

00:15:20.110 --> 00:15:24.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's still some time before 
the tea party begins. Please rest here.</font>

00:15:24.270 --> 00:15:26.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you. I will do that.</font>

00:15:29.640 --> 00:15:34.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Gyokuyou is getting sleepy often, 
a symptom of early pregnancy.</font>

00:15:35.740 --> 00:15:40.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What is the empress dowager thinking? 
Meeting outside the rear palace for tea?</font>

00:15:40.960 --> 00:15:45.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's outside the rear palace, but it's 
the inner court, where the emperor lives.</font>

00:15:45.770 --> 00:15:50.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's why it's scary! 
We never go there usually.</font>

00:15:50.160 --> 00:15:55.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The empress dowager knows 
Lady Gyokuyou is pregnant. So why now?</font>

00:15:55.660 --> 00:16:00.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're right, but I think we can trust
 the empress dowager to be careful about that.</font>

00:16:00.400 --> 00:16:04.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sure, the empress dowager will. But who 
knows what the other concubines will think?</font>

00:16:06.250 --> 00:16:09.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Lady Gyokuyou's pregnancy is an open secret,</i></font>

00:16:09.710 --> 00:16:14.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but at a face-to-face tea party, 
there could be a more direct probe.</i></font>

00:16:15.800 --> 00:16:20.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I guess Lady Lihua would avoid asking 
questions that could backfire on herself.</i></font>

00:16:21.540 --> 00:16:27.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Also, Lady Lihua is a proud woman. 
She wouldn't try to undercut others.</i></font>

00:16:27.670 --> 00:16:32.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It would also be a bad idea for Lady 
Gyokuyou to pick a fight with Lady Lihua,</i></font>

00:16:32.210 --> 00:16:33.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>since Lady Lihua has a more noble bloodline.</i></font>

00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:38.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Lady Lishu might say something 
if urged to do so by her ladies-in-waiting,</i></font>

00:16:38.680 --> 00:16:42.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but I doubt that head lady-in-waiting, 
the former taster, would step out of line.</i></font>

00:16:43.590 --> 00:16:45.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That leaves Concubine Loulan 
as the possibility.</i></font>

00:16:46.360 --> 00:16:50.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She's strangely free of rumors, aside from 
the well-known one about her flashy fashion.</i></font>

00:16:53.090 --> 00:16:55.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao, can I have a moment?</font>

00:16:57.510 --> 00:16:58.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:17:02.750 --> 00:17:04.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How may I help?</font>

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:09.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I will be the taster today. 
You understand what that means, right?</font>

00:17:10.430 --> 00:17:11.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, I do.</font>

00:17:12.770 --> 00:17:16.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>By not having a separate taster at a party 
set up by the empress dowager,</i></font>

00:17:16.750 --> 00:17:20.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>it demonstrates our trust in her.</i></font>

00:17:21.310 --> 00:17:23.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And, regarding you specifically,</font>

00:17:23.920 --> 00:17:27.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">the empress dowager would like 
your help with something.</font>

00:17:28.100 --> 00:17:30.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Have you been asked to solve a problem again?</font>

00:17:32.670 --> 00:17:36.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Did I... put a curse on the late emperor?</font>

00:17:37.450 --> 00:17:41.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'd like to speak to you elsewhere.</i></font>

00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:45.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't answer that, I know you can't tell me.</font>

00:17:45.460 --> 00:17:46.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However!</font>

00:17:46.890 --> 00:17:50.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please don't do anything 
to betray Lady Gyokuyou, all right?</font>

00:17:52.340 --> 00:17:55.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I have no desire to get on your 
bad side, Lady Hongniang.</font>

00:17:59.800 --> 00:18:04.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Good. I would also like to maintain 
a good relationship with you, Maomao.</font>

00:18:05.560 --> 00:18:06.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Indeed.</font>

00:18:07.390 --> 00:18:12.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Lady Hongniang really deserves the title 
of head lady-in-waiting for Lady Gyokuyou.</i></font>

00:18:17.170 --> 00:18:19.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If the empress dowager 
wants to discuss something,</i></font>

00:18:19.330 --> 00:18:20.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>it's most likely the curse she mentioned.</i></font>

00:18:25.140 --> 00:18:26.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you for waiting.</font>

00:18:27.120 --> 00:18:28.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This way.</font>

00:18:30.060 --> 00:18:34.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This used to serve the rear palace's function 
before the current rear palace was built.</font>

00:18:35.410 --> 00:18:36.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:18:38.600 --> 00:18:43.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There's nobody here, 
but the cleaning is impeccable.</i></font>

00:18:49.150 --> 00:18:52.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The pebbles on the dry landscape 
garden are well laid out, too.</i></font>

00:18:56.010 --> 00:18:57.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is the place.</font>

00:18:58.330 --> 00:19:00.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We can't go any further.</font>

00:19:00.120 --> 00:19:04.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Not even the cleaners 
are allowed to enter this place.</font>

00:19:13.370 --> 00:19:15.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What is this smell?</i></font>

00:19:15.960 --> 00:19:17.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What is this room...?</i></font>

00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:21.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">During the reign of our emperor's grandfather,</font>

00:19:21.530 --> 00:19:25.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">a court lady who became a
 low-ranking concubine lived here.</font>

00:19:27.380 --> 00:19:30.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This was the room of the woman 
who was referred to as the empress.</font>

00:19:30.130 --> 00:19:34.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This was also where the late emperor 
was raised, and where he passed away.</font>

00:19:38.890 --> 00:19:40.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's go somewhere else.</font>

00:19:54.220 --> 00:19:58.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">During his final years, the late emperor, 
and his mother, the so-called empress,</font>

00:19:58.890 --> 00:20:01.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">spent a lot of time in that room.</font>

00:20:02.930 --> 00:20:05.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">As if clinging to their memories, 
they spent much time there.</font>

00:20:05.520 --> 00:20:07.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The late emperor, 
perhaps due to a weakened spirit,</font>

00:20:08.370 --> 00:20:10.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">drew his last breath in that room,</font>

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:13.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">shortly after the empress died, 
as if chasing after her.</font>

00:20:13.770 --> 00:20:17.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This may sound rude, but he wasn't 
young when he passed away, right?</font>

00:20:17.850 --> 00:20:21.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He was old enough to be described 
as dying a natural death.</font>

00:20:21.160 --> 00:20:24.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Then why does the empress dowager 
think she cursed him?</i></font>

00:20:25.280 --> 00:20:28.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I also suggested to her that there is no curse.</font>

00:20:28.860 --> 00:20:30.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However, Lady Anshi said...</font>

00:20:31.210 --> 00:20:33.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I cursed him.</font>

00:20:33.230 --> 00:20:37.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wished he would go away. 
For the longest time...</font>

00:20:38.350 --> 00:20:40.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Almost every night, I wished for it.</font>

00:20:42.860 --> 00:20:47.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is there anything else to suggest 
that a curse was at play?</font>

00:20:49.470 --> 00:20:52.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The late emperor's body, 
after his spirit left it,</font>

00:20:52.170 --> 00:20:54.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">was placed in a mausoleum 
for a year as is customary.</font>

00:20:55.290 --> 00:21:02.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A year later, when our emperor and Lady 
Anshi took a look at the body to bury it...</font>

00:21:04.220 --> 00:21:09.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The body was almost exactly the same 
as when he had passed away.</font>

00:21:11.580 --> 00:21:14.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You mean there was no decay?</font>

00:21:14.540 --> 00:21:18.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Correct. The empress's body, who had 
passed away at around the same time,</font>

00:21:18.010 --> 00:21:21.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">was in a state that 
no words could describe. Yet...</font>

00:21:22.490 --> 00:21:26.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So that's why Lady Anshi thinks 
she cursed the late emperor.</font>

00:21:27.120 --> 00:21:28.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:21:28.680 --> 00:21:30.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I see.</i></font>

00:21:31.490 --> 00:21:36.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The mausoleum is chilly even 
in summer, but every corpse rots,</i></font>

00:21:36.620 --> 00:21:39.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>gets infested with insects, and dries out, 
unless it's placed in ice or something.</i></font>

00:21:40.330 --> 00:21:43.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If that didn't happen, 
that is indeed quite unusual.</i></font>

00:21:44.210 --> 00:21:46.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Everyone returns to dust in the end.</i></font>

00:21:46.920 --> 00:21:49.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's true for nobles, 
farmers, and everybody else.</i></font>

00:21:49.590 --> 00:21:53.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>No matter the status one is born into, 
that is the equalizer.</i></font>

00:21:54.950 --> 00:21:58.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That building will be torn down soon.</font>

00:21:58.320 --> 00:22:00.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We would like you to investigate 
before that happens.</font>

00:22:01.050 --> 00:22:02.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I understand.</font>

00:22:02.670 --> 00:22:05.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However, I have just one request.</font>

00:22:07.050 --> 00:22:07.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A request?</font>

00:23:45.020 --> 00:23:59.950
<font face="Times New Roman" size="22">{\an7}Next Time</font>

00:23:56.430 --> 00:23:59.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>{\an8}Next time: "The Late Emperor."</i></font>

00:23:56.490 --> 00:23:59.950
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}<font size="16">Episode 33: The Late Emperor</font></font>

